&lt;p&gt;Join Aya Healthcare, winner of multiple Top Workplace awards!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Account Manager will develop and manage new accounts for Educational services. He or she will proactively generate new business and strengthen existing client relationships, exceeding sales goals and offering exceptional client service.&lt;/p&gt;
